snippet.title: "Shut Your Mouth!" Judge Silences Amber Heard In Court!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is Silenced And Warned In Court For Her Inappropriate Behavior Towards Johnny And The Judge!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

From being Hollywood’s favorite couple to being one of the worst and most toxic couples to be in the spotlight, Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have been on the front page of news outlets for years now after Amber filed for divorce claiming Johnny was an abuser. What started as a romantic and cute relationship quickly turned violent and messy. But now 5 years after the initial divorce announcement, the couple is still in ongoing court battles and lawsuits even though the original divorce was actually concluded.

However recently, just a few weeks prior to their next defamation case court hearing, many things have started to come to light and there have been lots of changes in the situation. Which includes a massive win for Johnny Depp, apart from the most recent one where bodycam footage confirmed Amber was lying. This time it seems the Virginia judge who handles their case has had enough of Amber’s lies and doesn’t want to hear a single more. But what happened for her to reach this point? 

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
